  "text": "We run Bro as a network traffic analysis engine on a host equipped with two Intel Xeon E5-2670 processors clocked at 2.50 GHz for a total of 20 physical cores with 25.6MB of L3 cache for each processor and 4 x 10 Gbps SFP optical network interfaces. Traffic is load balanced onto a cluster of Bro nodes. (See [CITATION_1] for a description of Bro's cluster architecture.)",
